com.communote.plugins.api.rest.to

Class ApiResult<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.communote.plugins.api.rest.to.ApiResult<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - the capsuled resource
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class ApiResult<T>
extends Object
implements Serializable
    The resulting object of an api call is encapsulated into this class. A status defines if the call has been succeeded or not. The message gives an hint on the error case. The actual result object is stored in result.
    Author:
    Communote GmbH - http://www.communote.com/
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
